trans-unit.source: Specifies whether the target of a <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship"></xref> is inside or outside the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 지정 여부의 대상은 <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship"> </xref> 은 내부 또는 외부의 <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: If the target is inside the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package> (Internal), the relationship <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri%2A> is always a relative [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: 대상 안에 있으면는 <xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package>(내부) 관계 <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri%2A>는 항상 상대 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)].</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri%2A> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package>

trans-unit.source: If the target is outside the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package> (External), the relationship <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri%2A> can be either relative to the current location of the package or an absolute [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: 대상 범위를 벗어나는 경우는 <xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package>(외부) 관계 <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri%2A>패키지의 현재 위치에 대 한 상대 또는 절대 될 수 있습니다 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)].</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageRelationship.TargetUri%2A> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package>

trans-unit.source: The relationship references a resource that is external to the package.
trans-unit.target: 외부 패키지에 있는 리소스를 참조 하는 관계입니다.

trans-unit.source: The relationship references a part that is inside the package.
trans-unit.target: 관계는 패키지 내에 있는 부분을 참조 합니다.
